CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

December 7, 2006

[Cite as 121712006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-6383.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1000. Colonial Village Ltd. v. Washington Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 2004r-A-574. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to strike appellee Washington County Board of Revision and Washington County Auditor’s brief,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
